{"tid":1231474,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"In 長輩圖 we trust!!","createTime":"2019-06-16T12:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T13:07:23.000Z","uid":125210,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8ee4bdae444d0635120f581504c17d4a7abc68f6","tid":1231474,"uid":125210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:57:07.000Z","msg":"話說家中老母係典型港豬，加上政治冷感，平時同班師奶都係講下是非同咩地方有著數咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我都唔敢同佢講我69有上到街 費事佢又咦咦哦哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當晚佢見到電視咁多人上街 問我咩事<br />\n我send咗各位巴打既長輩圖比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又同佢解釋事情發生既前因後果<br />\n<br />\n點知今日比我見到佢同大陸朋友既對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUW77QH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUW77QH.png&h=da4eea7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u0r4qCp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu0r4qCp.png&h=4390ebc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MrWTiXq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMrWTiXq.png&h=00ceb25c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家真係唔好睇少長輩圖既威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個傳十個 十個就傳一百<br />\n希望大家可以將長輩圖send去家庭group 喚醒一個得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JOnZYYm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJOnZYYm.png&h=aa3c0041&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hy27op2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHy27op2.png&h=89461d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後想同我老母講聲：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">媽媽 我愛你啊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a68b6ca8b6e1f7fa9f38d21dd6378f5f3674241","tid":1231474,"uid":167692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}